## Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+ (LTS recommended)
- npm 9+

### Development

```bash
# Start development server
npm run dev
```

Server runs at `http://localhost:{{PORT}}/sse`

### Health Check

```bash
curl http://localhost:{{PORT}}/health
```

Expected: `{"status":"ok","service":"{{MCP_SERVER_NAME}}","version":"1.0.0"}`

## Testing

```bash
# Run all tests
npm run test:all

# Run unit tests only
npm run test:unit

# Run integration tests (requires dev server running)
npm run test:integration

# Generate coverage report
npm run test:coverage
```

## Deployment

```bash
# Deploy to Cloudflare Workers
npm run deploy
```

## Tools

This MCP server provides the following tools:

- **`health_check`** - Returns server health status
- **`echo`** - Echoes back the provided message (useful for testing)

